--Workflow--

Minute starts

Do necessary calculations to find parameters
Build the efficient frontier curve (4d(axes:%bobs,% aapl,% tsla, %expected_return) efficient frontier surface)
Pick the best portfolio composition based off of e(x) for surface
Move to a slightly more risk-averse position if risk_strat== risk_averse, stay constant if balanced, and to a more risk aggressive position if risk_strat == risk_agg
Identify differences in current composition and selected composition
Sell excess and buy missing
Adjust/recommend composition for trades based off the trades given manually from AI (if the news has been updated)
Update db, update portfolio value, update buying power and other helpful things necessary

Minute ends
Repeat
